# Template Workflow - User Guide

## Quick Start

Generate proposal templates from Deal Transfer Excel files with a single command.

```bash
/template generate deal <excel.xlsx>
```

## What It Does

Converts Deal Transfer Excel files into 3 proposal files:
- **Template** (`_template.md`) - Clean proposal for clients
- **Reasoning** (`_reasoning.md`) - Complete audit trail (internal)
- **Checklist** (`_checklist.md`) - Placeholders for presale confirmation

## Requirements

### Input
- ✅ Deal Transfer Excel file (`.xlsx` format)
- ✅ S1 (Commercial) sheet - Customer info, pain points, timeline
- ✅ S2 (Technical) sheet - Use cases, deployment, requirements

### Dependencies (Auto-Checked)
- ✅ Python 3
- ✅ pandas library
- ✅ openpyxl library

## Usage

### Basic Command

```bash
/template generate deal DT_0109.xlsx
```

